    <h1>ç”Ÿæ—¥å¿«ä¹ï¼Œæ—è¯—è¹ï¼</h1>
    
    <div class="image-container">
        < img src="https://qian-yue-lab.github.io/hello-world/birthday.jpg?v=999" alt="ç”Ÿæ—¥å›¾ç‰‡">
    </div>
    
    <div class="music-player">
        <p>ğŸµ SEVENTEEN - íƒœì–´ë‚˜ ì¤˜ì„œ ê³ ë§ˆì›Œ ğŸµ</p >
        
        <div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar">
            <div class="progress" id="progress"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="time">
            <span id="currentTime">0:00</span>
            <span id="duration">1:50</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="buttons">
            <button id="playBtn">æ’­æ”¾</button>
            <button id="pauseBtn">æš‚åœ</button>
            <button id="replayBtn">é‡æ’­</button>
        </div>
        
        <audio id="audio" loop>
            <source src="birthday.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
        </audio>
